          <title>
            <string language="en">Meaning of Colors</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Bedeutung von Farben</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Signification de couleurs</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Meaning das cores</string>

          </title>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="en">in this project the learners are going to investigate what is beautiful in paintings, colors and people. They will find materialon the web,organize it, get to some conclusions and finally present it in the class.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">english efl</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">vocabulary</string>
          </keyword>

          </keyword>

          </keyword>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">in diesem Projekt werden die Anfänger 
nachforschen, was in den Anstrichen, in den Farben und in den Leuten 
schön ist. Sie finden materialon das Web, organisieren es, 
gelangen an einige Zusammenfassungen und schließlich anwesend es in 
der Kategorie.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">dans ce projet les étudiants vont étudier ce 
qui est beau dans les peintures, les couleurs et les personnes. 
Ils trouveront le materialon le Web, l'organisent, obtiennent à
quelques conclusions et finalement il dans la classe.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">neste projeto os learners estão indo investigar 
o que é bonito nas pinturas, nas cores e nos povos. 
Encontrarão o materialon o Web, organizam-no, começam-no a 
algumas conclusões e finalmente atual ele na classe.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">in questo progetto i principianti stanno andando 
studiare che cosa è bello nelle pitture, nei colori e nella gente. 
Troveranno il materialon il Web, lo organizzano, ottengono ad 
alcune conclusioni ed infine presente esso nel codice categoria.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">σε αυτό το πρόγραμμα οι αρχάριοι πρόκειται να 
ερευνήσουν αυτό που είναι όμορφο στα έργα ζωγραφικής, τα 
χρώματα και τους ανθρώπους. Θα βρούν materialon τον Ιστό,
θα τον οργανώσουν, θα φτάσουν σε μερικά συμπεράσματα και τελικά 
παρών αυτό στην κλάση.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">en este proyecto los principiantes van a 
investigar cuál es hermoso en pinturas, colores y la gente. 
Encontrarán el materialon el Web, lo ordenan, consiguen a 
algunas conclusiones y finalmente presente él en la clase.</string>
          </description>
